Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.19,0:24:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Sorry, was eating gyōza.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:22.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6}I meant about the case.
